            "title": "AVAX One repurchases 2.42M shares",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>AVAX One Technology (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVX\" title=\"Avax One Technology Ltd.\">AVX</a></span>) on Thursday said it has repurchased an aggregate of 2.42M shares of its common stock under its authorized $40 million share repurchase program.</li>\n<li>AVX <span>+5.56%</span> premarket to $0.8002.</li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20425542-avax-one-repurchases-2423-383-shares-under-40-million-share-repurchase-program\">Press Release</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
